title: Brian Kendrick
summary: Brian David Kendrick (born May 29, 1979) is an American semi-retired professional wrestler and promoter. He is currently signed to WWE, where he performs on the NXT brand and works backstage as a producer. Kendrick is also known for his appearances with Ring of Honor (ROH), Total Nonstop Action Wrestling (TNA), New Japan Pro-Wrestling (NJPW), and Pro Wrestling Zero1 (Zero1).
